/svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rqq1665703136111.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqq1665703136111.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rqq1665703136111.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rqq1665703136111\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__u_printf_407621\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Print a formatted message to the Uniface transcript window.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__topic_d123071e1_d123072e1_d123073e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rqq1665703136111_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__codeblock_g1l_ntj_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">int u_printf (const char* format {,item {,item} ... });</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__topic_d87042e1_d87043e1_d87044e1_d87045e1_d87046e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d475540e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__parml_qvm_ptj_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">format</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">String containing the format, with or without conversion specifications</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">item</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Zero or more comma-separated arguments, as dictated by the\n                     <var class=\"keyword varname\">format</var> parameter</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__topic_d87047e1_d87048e1_d87049e1_d87050e1_d87051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d475540e93\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__p_d123089e1_d123090e1_d123091e1\">Like all members of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">printf</code> family, <code class=\"ph codeph\">u_printf</code> returns the length of the formatted string. In most cases this value is uninteresting, and you would typically call <code class=\"ph codeph\">u_printf</code> as if it were a <code class=\"ph codeph\">void</code> function.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__topic_d87052e1_d87053e1_d87054e1_d87055e1_d87056e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d475540e114\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__d6584e20\">Microsoft Windows platforms only. Library:\n          <span class=\"ph filepath\">ulib</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__topic_d87057e1_d87058e1_d87059e1_d87060e1_d87061e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d475540e127\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__p_d123101e1_d123102e1_d123103e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">u_printf</code> prints a formatted\n            message to the Uniface transcript window or transcript log file. The syntax of this\n            routine is equivalent to the standard C <code class=\"ph codeph\">printf</code> command. A full\n            description of all the formatting options available with <code class=\"ph codeph\">printf</code> is\n            outside the scope of this documentation. Consult your C compiler documentation or visit\n            the Microsoft DN documentation at: <a class=\"xref\" href=\"http://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/docs/\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/docs/</a>. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example prints a progress message in the transcript\n            window:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rqq1665703136111_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rqq1665703136111__codeblock_wdy_c5j_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">u_printf(\"Processing item %d out of %d/n\", counter, numitems);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531745\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531745\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "u_printf Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Print a formatted message to the Uniface transcript window. Explain this code int u_printf (const char* format {,item {,item} ... }); Copy Parameters format String containing the format, with or without conversion specifications item Zero or more comma-separated arguments, as dictated by the format parameter Return Values Like all members of the printf family, u_printf returns the length of the formatted string. In most cases this value is uninteresting, and you would typically call u_printf as if it were a void function. Use Microsoft Windows platforms only. Library: ulib Description u_printf prints a formatted message to the Uniface transcript window or transcript log file. The syntax of this routine is equivalent to the standard C printf command. A full description of all the formatting options available with printf is outside the scope of this documentation. Consult your C compiler documentation or visit the Microsoft DN documentation at: http://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/docs/ . The following example prints a progress message in the transcript window: Explain this code u_printf(\"Processing item %d out of %d/n\", counter, numitems); Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}